author: Staff report
title: Greetings From: Lansing
text: Posted Aug. 9, 2015 at 9:33 AM By Staff report Posted Aug. 9, 2015 at 9:33 AM Holland, Mich. The "Striders" of Evergreen Commons took a weekend trek to Lansing in June. During their three days there they explored the Michigan Historical Museum, toured the capital and met with Representative Daniela Garcia, walked the downtown river walk, visited the campus of Michigan State University, and toured the Turner-Dodge House and Fenner Nature Center. Send us your travel photos Send your scenic travel photo to lori.timmer@hollandsentinel.com or 54 W. Eighth St., Holland, MI 49423. Include information about your trip, as well as a contact number. By Staff report
